description:
A Head of Sales is now required as a result of business growth:

Responsibilities:

Manage P&L, and formulate & implement the sales strategies for both offline and online channels to achieve the business objectives;
Develop and drive the annual business plan based on the business dynamics;
Initiate the annual budget planning and control according to the business strategies ;
Lead the Hong Kong & Macau sales team to manage the key chains, direct sales and e-commerce channels;
Formulate the pricing strategies for the key accounts, e-business and direct sales channels to minimize channel conflicts and maximize profits;
Handle the key business partners directly including the retailers, distributors and service agencies;
Build relationships with the internal and external stakeholders including the cross-functional teams & business partners;
Conduct the market analysis to obtain business insight, and initiate the recommendation & business plans to drive business growth.

Requirements:

A degree in Business Administration or other related discipline;
A minimum of 10 years’ business development experience in the consumer health/ FMCG industries;
Experience in change management and with a track record in leading a sales team to achieve the sales targets;
Solid experience in e-commerce is an advantage;
Proficient in MS Excel, Word and Powerpoint;
A good team player with excellent leadership, analytical, negotiation and organizational skills;
Detail-minded, multi-tasking and result-driven with strong business acumen;
Effective time management skills and is able to work under pressure.
Thank you for your interest in a career with CK Life Sciences. Competitive compensation and benefits package will be offered to the right candidate. We operate a 5-day workweek, and our benefits cover retirement, health and life. Regular shuttle bus service is also provided with pick-ups and drop-offs at designated and convenient locations.

To apply for our position, you should write, enclosing a current resume to Chief Manager, Human Resources & Administration, CK Life Sciences Limited, 2 Dai Fu Street, Tai Po Industrial Estate, Hong Kong or by clicking the APPLY NOW button. For more company information, please visit www.ck-lifesciences.com. 

We are an equal opportunity employer and welcome applications from all qualified candidates.  Personal data collected will be treated in strictest confidence and handled confidentially by authorized personnel for recruitment-related purposes within the Group.

About the company

Our client is a leading FMCG company specialise in household products. They are looking for an experienced and mature Sales Manager to focus on General Trade sales management.

Responsibilities

Plan and implement sales strategies and promotions to achieve sales performance and growth;
Develop and maintain close relationship with wholesalers and drugstores; and account management;
Ensure quality service by frequent visits and understand the feedback from customers;
Collect market data to facilitate management strategic planning; and
Handle ad hoc duties as assigned

Requirements

Diploma holder in any discipline;
8 years' sales experience in general trade and drugstores in FMCG industries;
Good communication skill and negotiation skills, with ability to influence stakeholder and problem solving;
Proactive and independent with strong drive for sales achievement; and
Proficiency in English and Chinese

If you believe you have the right skills, attitude and experience please click 'apply now' below and upload your resume. Alternatively, for a confidential chat, please contact Vanessa Kan (Recruitment Consultant - Sales and Marketing) on +852 2232 3452.

Responsible for promoting IT Solutions and AI products to Public Utility and or Education sector;
Degree or diploma holder with at least 5 years’ sales experience in I.T. & AI solutions;
